{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/NLP/chatgpt_beyond/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Deep Learner","author":"[Jeonsworld]","siteUrl":"https:jeonsworld.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"jeonsworld/blog-comment"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":""}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"addfd3aa-6566-5c5b-85cd-fa9813479125","excerpt":"ChatGPT Beyond English: Towards a Comprehensive Evaluation of Large Language Models in Multilingual Learning\nViet Dac Lai, Nghia Trung Ngo, Amir Pouran Ben Veyseh, Hieu Man, Franck Dernoncourt, Trung Bui, Thien Huu Nguyen\nhttps://arxiv.org/abs/2304.05613 ChatGPT…","html":"<blockquote>\n<p><strong>ChatGPT Beyond English: Towards a Comprehensive Evaluation of Large Language Models in Multilingual Learning</strong>\nViet Dac Lai, Nghia Trung Ngo, Amir Pouran Ben Veyseh, Hieu Man, Franck Dernoncourt, Trung Bui, Thien Huu Nguyen\n<a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2304.05613\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2304.05613</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>ChatGPT는 이전보다 발전된 생성 능력을 갖추어 많은 관심을 받고 있음.</li>\n<li>ChatGPT는 영어기반 다양한 task에서 우수한 성능을 보여줌.</li>\n<li>하지만, 다른 언어에 대해서도 ChatGPT를 효과적으로 적용할 수 있는지에 대한 의문이 있으며, 이를 평가하기 위해 다양한 언어와 작업에 대한 평가가 필요.</li>\n<li>이를 위해 37개의 언어와 7가지 다른 NLP task에 대해 ChatGPT 평가를 수행.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>한국어가 포함된 downstream task 결과</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>개체명 인식\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 460px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 111.48648648648648%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"table1\"\n        title=\"table1\"\n        src=\"/static/3be0f3101e252305ec6b9cf13df47e23/08a84/table1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3be0f3101e252305ec6b9cf13df47e23/12f09/table1.png 148w,\n/static/3be0f3101e252305ec6b9cf13df47e23/e4a3f/table1.png 295w,\n/static/3be0f3101e252305ec6b9cf13df47e23/08a84/table1.png 460w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 460px) 100vw, 460px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></li>\n<li>관계 추출\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 471px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 129.05405405405406%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"table2\"\n        title=\"table2\"\n        src=\"/static/d5b5208d0db58f64aee2d283bf7ffc49/1f09d/table2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d5b5208d0db58f64aee2d283bf7ffc49/12f09/table2.png 148w,\n/static/d5b5208d0db58f64aee2d283bf7ffc49/e4a3f/table2.png 295w,\n/static/d5b5208d0db58f64aee2d283bf7ffc49/1f09d/table2.png 471w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 471px) 100vw, 471px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>결과</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>다른 NLP task와 언어에 대해서 ChatGPT의 성능이 이전 모델보다 나쁘게 나타났으며, 최적의 성능을 보장하기 위해 task에 specific한 모델을 개발해야 함을 제안.</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"ChatGPT Beyond English: Towards a Comprehensive Evaluation of Large Language Models in Multilingual Learning","date":"April 16, 2023"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/NLP/chatgpt_beyond/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/NLP/lecun_interview/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"AI 갓파더 얀 르쿤의 AI, LLM에 대한 인터뷰내용","category":"NLP","draft":false}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/NLP/rlforlm/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Reinforcement Learning for Language Model","category":"NLP","draft":false}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3128451518","96099027"]}